text: Please deliver my Kraken cooler early @FedEx can’t do my upgrades until I get that and you’re the final piece in the mail :D (Lol I wish).

Not exactly sure why my @FedEx package has to sit 7 miles from my house until ****ing Tuesday. Can’t build anything until I get that stupid package.

Uhhh, @FedEx, the shipping timeframe was based upon 1-3 business days. Not: “Uh, we don’t have to deliver today.” It’s been where it needs to go for 3 days and you simply won’t deliver it. Is it any wonder Americans hate shipping and cable companies?

And then just like that, somebody calls from my local @FedEx office and completely fixes the call center’s lack of customer service. I’m going to DM my case num so this employee can be recognized and rewarded.
@jorgesanchezkn Jorge, I'm glad to hear you received a call back in reference to the case that was created. I'll be happy to share your comments with manager of the agent who contacted you.
